PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Agriculture of Laurence Couture, of Saint-Anselme, Quebec, as a member of the Canadian Livestock Feed Board to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years or until the said Board is dissolved, whichever is earlier, in the place of Griffith T.
